  <summary>Launcher and package manager for RVGL</summary>
  <description>
    <p>RVGL Launcher is a cross-platform installer, launcher and package manager for RVGL, a cross-platform rewrite / port of Re-Volt that runs natively on a wide variety of platforms.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Install game and content packs and keep them up-to-date</li>
      <li>View list of online events and join them directly</li>
      <li>Enable or disable content packs on the fly</li>
      <li>Add your own content and repositories</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
